 of compelling evidence that a hailstorm was a contributory factor in the accident. The Mummy is a compelling movie that begins with a flashback to Imhotep's past. Jo went to a museum yesterday where she looked at every big nineteenth-century paintings in minute detail so as not to miss any wonderful things. She'll be giving a birthday party next Sunday in a hotel rather than at her home so as not to bother her neighboring homeowners."},{"pid":"033075f87c182ed0aaeb52ce7fa0908632be9180","tid":1687792,"uid":240608,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:13:09.000Z","msg":"樣貌 與年齡不符比例<br />\n<br />\n明明好後生 但老人臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1357dc774789878566e79427a1cef98d8d13483","tid":1687792,"uid":137569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7edbcbb5e5295e87f708454925c3c018f27f7c12","tid":1687792,"uid":75800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cbbb54a79b6db9625d9381dca0e4530710b3c061","tid":1687792,"uid":60831,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T05:42:13.000Z","msg":"冇波&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T05:43:52.000Z","msg":"白石媽媽就有波"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T13:03:33.000Z","msg":"白石媽媽正好多"},{"pid":"7981023d83e2b4e35f662345d7c87ec7fed0e547","tid":1687792,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35571f0e0bf00035da13abbd5e8c4af9668e0357","tid":1687792,"uid":75800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1357dc774789878566e79427a1cef98d8d13483","tid":1687792,"uid":137569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7edbcbb5e5295e87f708454925c3c018f27f7c12","tid":1687792,"uid":75800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cbbb54a79b6db9625d9381dca0e4530710b3c061","tid":1687792,"uid":60831,"like":3,"dislike":2,"